'From Squeak3.9alpha of ''2 November 2004'' [latest update: #6485] on 27 November 2004 at 11:55 am'!"Change Set:		DisableBaloonhelp-mdDate:			27 November 2004Author:			Marcus DenkerDisable ballon help. The system is unusable with this turnedon, as there is no delay between pointing to something and the balloonpopping up.As we are in alpha, this enables deprecation warnings, too."Preferences disable: #balloonHelpEnabled.Preferences enable: #showDeprecationWarnings.!